title: TV | Live Euro 2016 Qualifier - Ireland vs Germany
text: Ireland host Germany in this 7.45pm kick off at the Aviva stadium. The Republic produced a fine display in the reverse fixture to hold the world champions to a 1-1 draw thanks to John O'Shea's late equaliser. Three points would be an amazing result tonight, we'll more than happily take a draw again. While Germany have picked up form since their World Cup hangover, and should be a different beast in this fixture, Scotland recently showed weaknesses in their backline so we won't rule out the unlikely. #COYBIG
